          <p>CTO / COO / CO-FOUNDER</p>
          <p id="pforfounder">Ramakant plays a central role in driving all technological innovations that form the backbone of Homeland while also leading our operations team. Before founding Homeland, Ramakant was a core team member and Vice President of Engineering at Myntra, a leading fashion eCommerce startup in India (acquired by Flipkart). Ramakant, graduated from IIT Kanpur, and holds an MBA from Indian School of Business, Hyderabad.</p> 
