          <p id="pforfounder2">At Homeland, Anuj shapes the vision, strategy, and growth as we continuously redefine how interiors are designed and delivered. Formerly in the Silicon Valley, Anuj worked as the Global Head of Product Marketing for the eCommerce team at Google. A true citizen of the world, Anuj went to school at IIT Kanpur, received his MBA from the London Business School, and has lived in India, San Francisco, London, New York, and Singapore.</p>
